    <item>
      <title>中国向全球银行家征求反馈意见以提振市场信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/china-taps-global-bankers-for-feedback-to-lift-market-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国证券监管机构已增加与全球银行的互动频率，将原本每季度一次的讨论加强为有时每周一次或临时的询问，旨在收集对近期刺激措施的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/china-taps-global-bankers-for-feedback-to-lift-market-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 00:57:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
